      <p class="start-content">
        In badminton the racket is considered an extension of the player.
         When chosen appropriately it can enhance a players performance
          exorbitantly while when chosen poorly it can lead to otherwise
           avoidable blunders .<br>
        Thus the first step for any beginner-intermediate badminton player
         has to be to find their style and a racket that compliments it.<br> 
        So we are here to help you get  that first step in the bag !!!
        <br>
      </p>
