</div><br>
<li><span  class="prop-types">BALANCE</span> <br><br>When you are buying a badminton racket, there is one important thing that you should not ignore: the balance point of the racket.
    <br>
    The balance point is located along the shaft of the racket. It is simply a point at which you can balance the racket on your finger. Every racket feels different to you because of the balance point.
